40|$|Christine Morris stimulates, provokes, and {{challenges}} some fundamental axioms about culture and literature in her intriguing essay. The <b>absolutism</b> <b>of</b> her position forces readers to critically examine {{their own ideas}} about the transmission and preservation of culture. Ultimately, I have some skepticism about the <b>absolutism</b> <b>of</b> her position, but her paper moved me several steps towards her position and caused me to evaluate my ideas on other issues as well...|$|R
